  1. Introduction
  ---------------
    DOSINFO gives information about dos version, current date and time,
    graphic drive, BREAK and VERIFY settings, environment variables,
    free conventional memory, hard disk sizes and free spaces.

    The program runs on any IBM PC or compatible computer, under
    MS-DOS 3.30 or newer operating system.
    It needs about 40 kbytes of free (conventional) memory.

